<ul id="mwCW8"><li id="mwCXA">Boyd, Andrew, Joshua Comenetz. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=P1dly1ikblUC" id="mwCXE"><i id="mwCXI">An atlas of world affairs</i></a>. Routledge, 2007. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt643" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"0-415-39169-5"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCXM"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt643">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt643"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/0-415-39169-5" title="Special:BookSources/0-415-39169-5" about="#mwt643" id="mwCXQ">0-415-39169-5</a></li>
