<li id="mwCY8">Huffman, James L. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=pXe0zF1jd14C" id="mwCZA"><i id="mwCZE">Modern Japan: an encyclopedia of history, culture, and nationalism</i></a>. Taylor &amp; Francis, 1998. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt673" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"0-8153-2525-8"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCZI"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt673">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt673"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/0-8153-2525-8" title="Special:BookSources/0-8153-2525-8" about="#mwt673" id="mwCZM">0-8153-2525-8</a></li>
