<li id="mwCZc">Nock, Albert Jay. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=zQoMAAAAYAAJ" id="mwCZg">The Myth of a Guilty Nation</a>. B.W. Huebsch, Incorporated, 1922.</li>
<li id="mwCZk">Bakeless, John Edwin. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=5wgAAAAAYAAJ" id="mwCZo"><i id="mwCZs">The Economic Causes of Modern War; A Study of the Period: 1878–1918</i></a>. New York: Printed for the Department of political science of Williams college, by Moffat, Yard and Co, 1921</li>
